      {
        "claim_id": "claim_7df79277",
        "status": "unsupported",
        "support_ids": [],
        "text": "Two entries carry [VERIFY] tags introduced in v1.2 and preserved verbatim in v1.3: Simmhan, Plale, and Gannon (2005) is the reference added in response to the 2026-05-23 Technical-auditor finding that \u00a72.3 cited the work without a References entry; the citation is restored with [VERIFY] on pagination and DOI because the entry was not independently confirmed in-session via OpenAlex or the ACM Digital Library, and the resolution of that tag is a pre-submission step."
      },
      {
        "claim_id": "claim_de104ff3",
        "status": "unsupported",
